These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-1::.
3 different games are played: poker, whist, go
House: tower, victorian, townhouse
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, aquamarine, amber
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, puzzles, baking
City: berlin, liverpool, hannover
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, davidoff, oliveros
 1. the victorian house is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the right of the person who likes amber##8
 3. the person playing go is not to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##8
 4. the person who likes azure is the person traveling to hannover##1
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
 6. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5
 8. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 9. the victorian house is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
10. the davidoff-smoker is not to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
11. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the right of the victorian house##8
13. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere between the person who likes amber and the person playing poker##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Game          | poker | whist | go    |
| House           | tower | victorian   | townhouse     |
| Color   | azure     | aquamarine   | amber       |
| Hobby   | puzzles    | baking   | filmmaking     |
| City   | hannover    | berlin   | liverpool |
| Cigar     | oliveros     | alhambra | davidoff     |

